<div class="tracker-agent-panel">
  <header class="tracker-agent-header">
    <div class="tracker-agent-header-labels">
      <span class="tracker-agent-header-title">Agent</span>
      <span class="tracker-agent-header-hint">Tracker</span>
    </div>
    <button
      type="button"
      class="tracker-agent-panel-close"
      id="tracker-agent-panel-close"
      aria-label="Close assistant panel"
    >
      <span aria-hidden="true">×</span>
    </button>
  </header>
  <div class="tracker-agent-thread" id="tracker-agent-thread" role="log" aria-live="polite">
    <div class="tracker-agent-welcome" id="tracker-agent-welcome">
      <p class="tracker-agent-welcome-title">비행 어시스턴트</p>
      <p class="tracker-agent-welcome-text">
        인사·잡담도 되고, 비행 데이터는 Analyze 후 더 잘 맞춰요.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="tracker-agent-messages" id="tracker-agent-messages" hidden></div>
  </div>
  <div class="tracker-agent-composer">
    <label class="tracker-agent-sr-only" for="tracker-agent-input">Message</label>
    <textarea
      id="tracker-agent-input"
      class="tracker-agent-input"
      rows="3"
      placeholder="메시지를 입력…"
      autocomplete="off"
    ></textarea>
    <div class="tracker-agent-composer-actions">
      <button type="button" class="button button-primary tracker-agent-send" id="tracker-agent-send" disabled>
        Send
      </button>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
